thread.title: Gary Edgar
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Gary Edgar

author: Gary Edgar
title: Gary Edgar
text: When OEM replacement cartridges cost more than the budget printer, you need an alternative and Ink Station is just the ticket. Cartridges half the price of genuine ones, fast delivery and best of all unlike some cheap generics that cause the printer to hiccup, these ones work fine. Excellent value all round.
